# Feature 041 sprint 04: @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk requires zod@^4 as a
# peer. The backend pins zod@^3.23.8 (zod@3.25+ ships a `zod/v4` subpath that
# the SDK uses — so both APIs coexist inside one package). npm's strict peer
# resolution doesn't know that, so we opt into legacy-peer-deps here. Local
# dev + CI + Railway Dockerfile all honor this.
legacy-peer-deps=true
